I"ž<p>I accidently found a nifty way of calling <del datetime="2009-11-04T09:19:06+00:00">class</del> singleton methods. Imagine you have this code:</p>

<pre>

class FoundANewWay
    def self.to_call_a_singleton_method
        puts "It works!"
    end
end
</pre>

<p>and you can call it like this:</p>

<pre>
FoundANewWay.to_call_a_singleton_method

or

FoundANewWay::to_call_a_singleton_method
</pre>

<p>Cool!</p>
:ET